edu.wpi.cs.wpisuitetng.network.models

Interface IRequest

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MockRequest, MockRequest, Request, RequestModel

    public interface IRequest
    An interface for providing information regarding a network request. This interface allows for RequestObserver to be a superclass of Request while preventing the need for developers to cast a RequestObserver to a Request inside their responseSuccess, responseError and fail methods.
